longBusinessSummary: Röko AB (publ) is a private equity firm specializes in small- and medium-sized businesses. The firm prefers to invest in B2B and B2C markets. The firm focuses on Europe region. It typically investments in companies with EBITDA between 2 million ($21.40 million) and 10 million ($107.4 million) along with margin of at least 10%. Röko AB (publ) was founded in 2019 and is headquartered in Stockholm, Sweden.
